	<p><strong>Research interests</strong></p>
	<ul><li><p> Guaranteeing the safety and preserving the concurrency for <u>automatic concurrent bug fixing</u> (with the discrete control theory)</p></li></ul>
	<ul><li><p> Identifying a balance point between the expressiveness and simplicity of <u>atomicity specification</u></p></li></ul>
	<ul><li><p> Optimizing the <u>object persistence</u> by guiding it in an intelligent way</p></li></ul>
	<ul><li><p> <u>Record and Replay</u></p></td></li></ul>
